{"tid":292633,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一張圖  關於學英文既速度","createTime":"2017-06-21T13:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T15:27:59.000Z","uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54547ffcd429d64edbf1ebd99f550259ee73127b","tid":292633,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n唔記得係咪向FACEBOOK到見過<br />\n<br />\n構圖好簡單  左一半右一半<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都係有隻狗<br />\n<br />\n左邊係飲水喉流出黎既自來水  比喻向香港既學校學英文<br />\n<br />\n右邊係飲球場灑力射水器既水  比喻去外國讀書時學英文<br />\n<br />\n全能既連登神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2734e2f97aed880383061b3a9e25cdf22f0eadb","tid":292633,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c15248cb3081f4fb7938ff773b8eb45ea10b547","tid":292633,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0094043632a2505f1abc27ca43776a0dbb3f691d","tid":292633,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4dcdf3d54120f836d72d0e0bad3c9128ad2e4605","tid":292633,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n推10次就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797d0f4eb86d4e80560d03c6accbbb96177a1b98","tid":292633,"